NHL Game Boxscore

nhl_game_boxscore.Rd

Returns information on game boxscore for a given game id

nhl_game_boxscore(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

Game unique ID

Value

Returns a named list of data frames: team_box, players_box, skaters, goalies, on_ice, on_ice_plus, penalty_box, scratches, team_coaches

Examples

# \donttest{
  nhl_game_boxscore(game_id=2021020182)
